	<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 29.05pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">根据</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">工业和信息化部《关于印发〈<SPAN lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN>年工业节能监察重点工作计划〉的通知》（工信部节函〔<SPAN lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN>〕<SPAN lang=EN-US>95</SPAN>号）</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">的要求，由国家工信部、江苏省节能监察中心、苏州市节能监察中心等单位派员组成的专项监察组，于<SPAN lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN>年<SPAN lang=EN-US>5</SPAN>月<SPAN lang=EN-US>11</SPAN>、<SPAN lang=EN-US>12</SPAN>日对我市台玻长江玻璃有限公司、台玻昆山玻璃有限公司开展了现场节能监察。<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.05pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">监察组主要核查了企业</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312">单位产品能耗核算及达标情况；企业能源计量、统计及能源回收利用情况；核实各能源品种折标系数是否符合有关标准规定；企业能源管理制度和能源管理体系建设情况；节能措施和节能项目实施情况；企业能源利用存在的问题及整改措施等。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋">经现场核查、现场核算，<SPAN style="COLOR: black; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">台玻长江玻璃有限公司、台玻昆山玻璃有限公司</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>2016</SPAN>年</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">综合能源消费单位产品综合能耗、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋">平板玻璃单位熔窑热耗等指标均达到《平板玻璃单位产品能源消耗限额》（<SPAN lang=EN-US>GB21340-2013</SPAN>）中</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">平板玻璃单位产品综合能耗≤<SPAN lang=EN-US>14k</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋" lang=EN-US>gce/</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋">重量箱，平板玻璃单位熔窑热耗</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">≤</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋" lang=EN-US>6700kJ/kg</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋">的限定值要求。同时要求企业采取切实可行的节能低碳技术，从而进一步降低能耗。<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
